    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "I didn't even realize how thirsty I was during doing all that. I filled up my water supply at a public tap, then I bought a liter of orange juice and a baguette. I finished the liter right on the spot.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "The sun was still high. I decided to go until Auvillar. That was the right decision because the track was super nice. First along the canal, then south on a very small country road lined with strange trees. These 15km are now number 1 in my guidebook. Auvillar showed off with some impressive views over the Garonne valley.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
