  }, "The night wasn't particularly quiet, but I still slept quite a lot. Up at 7. Sun, blue sky. A warm climate is definitely a monetary benefit. Morning routine: going to the toilet, inserting lenses, \"washing\" with wet wipes, brushing my teeth, sunscreen. Then breakfast: muesli. When the mug was free again, tea, and baguette with butter and honey.", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "At half past eight I made my way to Pau. 90 km. I was hoping to find an Internetcaf\xE9 there with nightly opening hours for skyping. I also wanted to send things home. Too many tools. What I hadn't needed by now could be solved later without those tools as well. In the mountains I wanted to take it easy on my body and preferred to trust my solid bike...", mdx("br", {
    parentName: "p"
  }), "\n", "So I mused to myself, turned around a bend and \u2013 there they were: sunlit, snow-covered and, above all, high! The mountains. Intimidating at first. After 80 km, however, I had gotten used to the sight and found them inviting, the Pyrenees.")), mdx("p", null, mdx("span", {
